log_probs = F.log_softmax(preds, dim=-1)
        probs = torch.exp(log_probs)
        labels = labels.view(-1)
        log_p_t = log_probs[range(preds.size(0)), labels]
        p_t = probs[range(preds.size(0)), labels]
        if self.alpha.device != preds.device:
            self.alpha = self.alpha.to(preds.device)
        alpha_t = self.alpha[labels]
        loss = -alpha_t * (1 - p_t) ** self.gamma * log_p_t
        if self.size_average:
            loss = loss.mean()
        else:
            loss = loss.sum()
        return loss
